  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 5 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0 \u0bae\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Central Bank resolution to permanently terminate the activities of 5 defunct finance companies",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Monetary Board of the Central Bank of Sri Lanka has permanently demarcated the Bank of Sri Lanka by permanently concluding the operations of 5 defunct finance companies consisting of Senral Investment and Finance Limited, ERI Finance Limited, RKS Finance Limited, The Finance Public Company and The Stranded Credit Finance Limited.",
        "The Monetary Board of the Central Bank of Sri Lanka has renewed the branding of 5 disrupted finance companies, namely Chenral Investment and Finance Limited, ERI Finance Limited, RKS Finance Limited, The Finance Public Company and The Stranded Credit Finance Limited.",
        "Accordingly, the Committee was tasked by the Monetary Board to make the necessary recommendations for the revival of the companies and to recommend the permanent termination of the activities of the companies when it is not possible to implement them.",
        "In this context, the Committee submitted its final report to the Monetary Board on 31st of last month after considering the recommendations submitted by various parties for revival of 4 of the above companies.",
        "After reviewing the report, the Monetary Board ruled that the recommendations made to the Committee were not feasible and could not be implemented under the current framework as they contain a variety of policy and legal obligations.",
        "Therefore, since the only solution is to permanently terminate the operations of these 5 defunct companies, action will be taken to bring it within the relevant legal frameworks, the report said."
      ],
